HEADWORD: Stomachy
<hw>Stom"ach*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Obstinate; sullen;
haughty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A little, bold, solemn, <qex>stomachy</qex> man, a great professor
of piety.</q> <rj><qau>R. L. Stevenson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stomapod</ent>⟦br⟧
